STATE
v.
William Henry RAINES. No. 211A06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 20, 2007. Jonathan E. Broun, Durham, for Raines. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Joan Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of NC.
